{%- comment -%}
  /**
   * Dynamic Promo Blocks Section
   *
   * A flexible promotional banner system featuring asymmetric grid layout
   * with one large left module and three smaller right modules for showcasing
   * products, offers, and promotional content with rich customization options.
   *
   * FEATURES:
   * - Asymmetric grid layout (1 large + 3 small modules)
   * - Responsive design with separate desktop/mobile layouts
   * - Multi-language support (English, German, French, Finnish)
   * - Individual background images for desktop and mobile
   * - Customizable content positioning within each module
   * - Tag/badge system for promotional labels
   * - Call-to-action buttons with custom styling
   * - Background image controls (size, position)
   * - Typography customization (size, color)
   *
   * LAYOUT STRUCTURE:
   * Desktop:
   * - Left: 1 large promotional module (50% width)
   * - Right: 3 smaller modules in 2x2 grid (50% width)
   *   - Top: 1 medium module (full width)
   *   - Bottom: 2 small modules (side by side)
   *
   * Mobile:
   * - Stacked vertical layout
   * - Left module displayed first
   * - Only first right module shown (modules 2&3 hidden)
   *
   * RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR:
   * - Desktop: CSS Grid layout with asymmetric columns
   * - Mobile: Vertical stacking with simplified content
   * - Adaptive font sizes and spacing
   * - Separate mobile background images
   * - Content repositioning for mobile optimization
   *
   * LOCALIZATION:
   * - Multi-language text support for all content elements
   * - Automatic language detection based on request locale
   * - Fallback to default language when translations unavailable
   * - Supported languages: EN, DE, FR, FI
   *
   * CUSTOMIZATION OPTIONS:
   * - Section height control (desktop/mobile)
   * - Background images (desktop/mobile variants)
   * - Background size and positioning
   * - Content vertical positioning (top/center/bottom)
   * - Tag/badge text and styling
   * - Title text with custom typography
   * - Button text, URLs, and color schemes
   * - Background colors for each module
   *
   * MODULE CONFIGURATION:
   * - Left Module: Large promotional space with prominent title
   * - Right Module 1: Medium-sized featured content
   * - Right Module 2: Small promotional block
   * - Right Module 3: Small promotional block
   *
   * CONTENT ELEMENTS:
   * - Promotional tags/badges with custom styling
   * - Multi-language titles with responsive typography
   * - Call-to-action buttons with hover effects
   * - Background overlays for text readability
   *
   * TECHNICAL FEATURES:
   * - CSS custom properties for dynamic styling
   * - Liquid template variables for localization
   * - Responsive image handling with multiple sizes
   * - CSS Grid and Flexbox for layout control
   * - Hover effects and transitions
   *
   * DEFAULT PRESET:
   * - "Dynamic Promo Blocks" with sample content
   * - Pre-configured layout and styling
   *
   * DEPENDENCIES:
   * - Shopify Liquid template engine
   * - Modern CSS (Grid, Flexbox, Custom Properties)
   * - Responsive image processing
   *
   * BROWSER SUPPORT:
   * - Modern browsers with CSS Grid support
   * - Progressive enhancement for older browsers
   * - Mobile-first responsive design
   */
{%- endcomment -%}

